{
  "texts": [
    "Of these, 58 agreed to participate in the study, while one PST opted out of having their work included in the study.",
    "The data were collected from the 58 PSTs' assignment submissions of the course.",
    "All the submissions were from one cohort of PSTs.",
    "The relevant University and School authorities provided ethical protocols to collect PSTs' archived assignment data with approval number ETH2023-0208.",
    "The participants included PSTs with low socio-economic status (n=6), Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islanders (n=2), PSTs with English as an additional language (n=4) and PSTs with disability (n=9)."
  ]
}